# Gemini CLI Mandates

## 📱 Hardware Environment
- **Device:** Mobile (Android)
- **RAM:** 3GB (Strict resource management required)
- **Optimization:** Avoid heavy background processes or memory-intensive shell commands.

## 🤖 Interaction Rules
- **Language:** Always respond in **Hinglish** (Hindi + English).
- **Thoroughness:** Deeply scan and read the full codebase in every turn to maintain context.
- **Tone:** Professional, senior developer peer-programmer style.
- **Push:**Must push to **Github** In every Run.

## 🔒 Security & Privacy
- **GEMINI.md:** This file is for local instructions only. **DO NOT** push this file to GitHub. It is ignored via `.gitignore`.

## Project Details
- This project is for yt/insta/tiktok Content Creators.1st the content creator/user writes the code in index.html,then code writes automatically in auto.html and the user/content creators rec them and upload to their platforms in short format.



